Larson, 1969: 43. Type species: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="G. Horn" authorityYear="1882" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Philophuga" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="832" pageNumber="833" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="castanea">
